descript.abstract: This data displays the bathymetry of the Southeast Asia region. The original dataset used to make this data is the "Measured and estimated seafloor topography" and the Land Topography comes from GTOPO30. This dataset was clipped to the boundaries of Indonesia for use in the Interactive Atlas of Indonesia's Forests (2009).
